dit |title=No, Andrew Bogut's injury is not a conspiracy |last=Mustard |first=Extra |date=2016-12-30 |work=[[運動畫刊|Sports Illustrated]] |access-date=2016-12-31 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102142632/http://www.si.com/extra-mustard/2016/12/30/andrew-bogut-knee-injury-pizzagate-conspiracy-reddit |archive-date=2017-01-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://mashable.com/2016/12/30/bogut-pizzagate-nba-injury-conspiracy/ |title=Conspiracy theorists think an injured NBA player is another victim of Pizzagate |last=Knoblauch |first=Max |date=2016-12-30 |access-date=2016-12-31 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230230303/http://mashable.com/2016/12/30/bogut-pizzagate-nba-injury-conspiracy/ |archive-date=2016-12-30 |publisher=[[Mashable|Mashable]]}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Elon University|伊隆大學}}媒體分析助理教授喬納森·奧爾布賴特（{{lang|en|Jonathan Albright}}）表示在[[捷克|捷克]]、[[賽普勒斯|賽普勒斯]]和[[越南|越南]]關於披薩門的推文特別多，而當中最頻繁轉推的人是[[網路機器人|網路機器人]]<ref name="fromrumor">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/pizzagate-from-rumor-to-hashtag-to-gunfire-in-dc/2016/12/06/4c7def50-bbd4-11e6-94ac-3d324840106c_story.html |title=Pizzagate: From rumor, to hashtag, to gunfire in D.C. |last=Fisher |first=Marc |date=2016-12-06 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |access-date=2016-12-23 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220201405/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/pizzagate-from-rumor-to-hashtag-to-gunfire-in-dc/2016/12/06/4c7def50-bbd4-11e6-94ac-3d324840106c_story.html |archive-date=2016-12-20 |last2=Cox |first2=John Woodrow |last3=Hermann |first3=Peter}}</ref>。

Reddit社群/r/The_Donald的網民開了/r/pizzagate看板來繼續討論陰謀論<ref name="NYT" />。在用戶發布跟陰謀相關人員的詳細資料後，看板因違反Reddit的反[[人肉搜尋|人肉搜尋]]政策而於2016年11月23日遭到封鎖。Reddit之後發表聲明表示「我們不想在我們網站上進行獵巫活動」<ref name=bbc-pizzagate /><ref name="WP">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2016/11/23/fearing-yet-another-witch-hunt-reddit-bans-pizzagate/ |title=Fearing yet another witch hunt, Reddit bans 'Pizzagate' |last=Ohlheiser |first=Abby |date=2016-11-24 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |access-date=2016-11-25 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230234312/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2016/11/23/fearing-yet-another-witch-hunt-reddit-bans-pizzagate/ |archive-date=2016-12-30}}</ref>。在遭到Reddit封鎖後，討論群移師到與Reddit相同性質的網站[[Voat|Voat]]的v/pizzagate看板<ref name="robertas" />。

陰謀論支持者包括[[大衛·西曼|-{zh-hans:大卫·西曼;zh-hk:大衛·施文;zh-tw:大衛·西曼;}-]]和小麥可·-{zh-hans:弗林;zh-hant:弗林;zh-tw:佛林;}-（{{lang|en|Michael G. Flynn}}，[[迈克尔·T·弗林|迈克尔·-{zh-hans:弗林;zh-hant:弗林;zh-tw:佛林;}-]]的兒子）將這一陰謀演變成更深層次的政府陰謀，並稱之為「戀童門」（{{lang|en|Pedogate}}）。根據這一理論，[[新世界秩序_(陰謀論)|新世界秩序]]的「撒但菁英陰謀集團」正在經營著國際兒童性販賣團體<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.esquire.com/news-politics/news/a54126/pizzagate-will-never-die/ |title=Pizzagate Will Never Die: Here's Why the Conspiracy Theory Has New Life |last=Wade |first=Peter |date=2017-03-25 |work=[[君子雜誌|Esquire]] |access-date=2017-03-26 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170325214047/http://www.esquire.com/news-politics/news/a54126/pizzagate-will-never-die/ |archive-date=2017-03-25}}</ref>。

===土耳其新聞稿===
[[土耳其|土耳其]]的一些親政府報紙（即支持總統[[雷傑普·塔伊普·艾爾多安|雷傑普·塔伊普·-{zh-hans:埃尔多安;zh-hant:埃爾多安;zh-tw:艾爾多安;}-]]）報導這項指控，包括《{{tsl|en|Sabah (newspaper)|沙巴報}}》、《{{tsl|en|A Haber|A Haber}}》、《{{tsl|en|Yeni Şafak|新黎明報}}》、《{{tsl|en|Akşam|晚間報 (土耳其)|晚間報}}》和《{{tsl|en|Star (Turkish newspaper)|星報 (土耳其)|星報}}》。陰謀論也有出現在土耳其的{{tsl|en|Ekşi Sözlük|Ekşi Sözlük}}網站以及任何人都能發布內容的新聞網HaberSelf。論壇中直接重新發佈早已被刪除的Reddit子板中的影像和指控，而這些影像和指控被國營媒體完整地重印出來<ref name=bbc-pizzagate/><ref name="Daily Dot">{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailydot.com/layer8/pizzagate-alt-right-turkey-trolls-child-abuse/ |title=How the alt-right's PizzaGate conspiracy hid real scandal in Turkey |last=Sozeri |first=Efe Karem |date=2016-11-23 |access-date=2016-12-13 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202003856/http://www.dailydot.com/layer8/pizzagate-alt-right-turkey-trolls-child-abuse/ |archive-date=2016-12-02 |publisher=The Daily Dot}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|The Daily Dot|每日點選}}》的專欄作家埃菲·索澤里（{{lang|en|Efe Sozeri}}）提出土耳其政府相關人士一直報導該陰謀論，是想分散人們對2016年3月在當地發生的虐待兒童醜聞的注意力<ref name="Daily Dot" />。

==遭到騷擾的餐廳老闆和員工==
[[File:Comet-ping-pong-pizza-pizzagate-podesta-brock.jpg|thumb]]

隨著披薩門的發酵，彗星乒乓遭到上百名披薩門陰謀論支持者恐嚇<ref name="Reilly">{{Cite news |url=http://fortune.com/2016/11/22/comet-ping-pong-hillary-clinton-fake-news/ |title=Washington Pizza Place Flooded With Threats Over False Hillary Clinton Conspiracy |last=Reilly |first=Katie |date=2016-11-22 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217164734/http://fortune.com/2016/11/22/comet-ping-pong-hillary-clinton-fake-news/ |archive-date=2017-02-17 |publisher=[[财富_(杂志)|Fortune]]}}</ref>。餐廳的老闆{{tsl|en|James Alefantis|詹姆斯·阿萊凡蒂斯}}告訴《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》：「就是因為這個荒唐又捏造的陰謀論，我們一直受到攻擊。這幾天我什麼都沒做，就只有嘗試澄清以及保護員工和朋友免受威脅。」<ref name="NYT" />

一些陰謀論支持者找到了阿萊凡蒂斯的[[Instagram|Instagram]]帳戶，並指他發布的某些照片就是陰謀的證據。許多朋友和家人的相片因為讚好了彗星乒乓的[[Facebook|Facebook]]專頁而被公諸於眾。更有一些圖像被截取自不相關的網站，並被訛稱由阿萊凡蒂斯所拍攝<ref name="snopes">{{Cite web |url=http://www.snopes.com/pizzagate-conspiracy/ |title=A detailed conspiracy theory known as "Pizzagate" holds that a pedophile ring is operating out of a Clinton-linked pizzeria called Comet Ping Pong |last=LaCapria |first=Kim |date=2016-12-02 |publisher=Snopes.com |access-date=2020-09-05 |archive-date=2021-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125225946/https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/pizzagate-conspiracy/ }}</ref>。餐廳老闆和員工均在社交媒體上受到騷擾和恐嚇，而老闆甚至收到死亡威脅<ref name="NYT">{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/21/technology/fact-check-this-pizzeria-is-not-a-child-trafficking-site.html |title=Fake News Onslaught Targets Pizzeria as Nest of Child-Trafficking |last=Kang |first=Cecilia |date=2016-11-21 |work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208232606/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/21/technology/fact-check-this-pizzeria-is-not-a-child-trafficking-site.html |archive-date=2016-12-08}}</ref>。餐廳的[[Yelp|Yelp]]被網站營運商封鎖，指評論「更多是針對新聞報導本身，而不是評論者的個人消費體驗」<ref name="snopes" />。

幾個曾在披薩店演出的樂團也面臨騷擾。例如，{{tsl|en|Heavy Breathing|沉重呼吸樂團}}的阿曼達·克萊曼（{{lang|en|Amanda Kleinman}}）在收到她和樂團與陰謀論有關係的惡意評論後刪掉了Twitter帳戶<ref name="NYT" />。另一個樂團{{tsl|en|Sex Stains|性污漬}}關閉了他們[[YouTube|YouTube]]影片的留言區，並在視頻資訊欄下解釋爭議<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://dcist.com/2016/12/what_on_earth_is_pizzagate_why_did.php |title=What On Earth Is Pizzagate And How Did It Result In Gunfire At Comet Ping Pong? |last=Tempey |first=Nathan |date=2016-12-05 |access-date=2016-12-10 |dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208075242/http://dcist.com/2016/12/what_on_earth_is_pizzagate_why_did.php |archive-date=2016-12-08 |publisher=DCist}}</ref>。藝術家阿靈頓·德迪奧尼索（{{lang|en|Arrington de Dionyso}}）曾在發生爭議前幾年在披薩店畫過壁畫，其詳細描述了針對他的騷擾活動<ref name="Arrington de Dionyso essay.">{{Cite web |url=https://medium.com/@arringtond/how-i-became-a-target-of-the-alt-right-66f14eceaffe#.44155m5pk |title=How I became a target of the alt-right What it's like to be targeted by Neo-Nazis and supporters of Donald Trump online and what I learned from it. |last=de Dionyso |first=Arrington |date=2016-12-13 |publisher=[[Medium|Medium]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711132950/https://medium.com/%40arringtond/how-i-became-a-target-of-the-alt-right-66f14eceaffe#.44155m5pk |archive-date=2017-07-11}}</ref>，並表示：「我覺得這些攻擊非常刻意，而最終將（會變成）對所有自由表達形式進行的協同攻擊。」這次事件被用以跟[[玩家門|玩家門爭議]]進行比較<ref name="Arrington de Dionyso interview">{{Cite web |url=http://hyperallergic.com/347458/artist-targeted-by-pizzagate-conspiracy-theory-speaks/ |title=Artist Targeted by #Pizzagate Conspiracy Theory Speaks |last=Murphy |first=Blair |date=2016-12-22 |publisher=Hyperallergic |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225140915/http://hyperallergic.com/347458/artist-targeted-by-pizzagate-conspiracy-theory-speaks/ |archive-date=2016-12-25}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.spin.com/2016/12/what-is-pizzagate-the-insane-child-sex-conspiracy-theory-that-led-a-man-to-fire-a-rifle-in-a-restaurant-explanied/ |title=What Is Pizzagate? The Insane Child Sex Conspiracy Theory That Led a Man to Fire a Rifle in a Restaurant, Explained |last=Cush |first=Andy |date=2016-12-05 |access-date=2016-12-29 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229042945/http://www.spin.com/2016/12/what-is-pizzagate-the-insane-child-sex-conspiracy-theory-that-led-a-man-to-fire-a-rifle-in-a-restaurant-explanied/ |archive-date=2016-12-29 |publisher=Spin}}</ref>。

