因披薩門受到騷擾的公司不僅限於彗星乒乓，其他像與乒乓三店之隔的野獸披薩（{{lang|en|Besta Pizza}}）、小紅狐咖啡店（{{lang|en|Little Red Fox cafe}}）、{{tsl|en|Politics and Prose|政治與散文}}書店以及泰拉索法式小酒館（{{lang|en|French bistro Terasol}}）等其他位於哥倫比亞特區的公司也同樣如此<ref name="salon20161206">{{Cite news |url=http://www.salon.com/2016/12/06/pizzagate-harassment-spreads-beyond-comet-ping-pong-to-nearby-d-c-restaurants/ |title=Pizzagate harassment spreads beyond Comet Ping Pong to nearby D.C. restaurants |last=Gauthier |first=Brendan |date=2016-12-07 |work=Salon |access-date=2016-12-08 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207154719/http://www.salon.com/2016/12/06/pizzagate-harassment-spreads-beyond-comet-ping-pong-to-nearby-d-c-restaurants/ |archive-date=2016-12-07}}</ref><ref name="Kludt">{{Cite news |url=https://money.cnn.com/2016/12/05/media/pizzagate-threatening-calls-washington-dc-businesses/ |title='Pizzagate': Comet Ping Pong not the only D.C. business enduring a nightmare |last=Kludt |first=Tom |date=2016-12-05 |access-date=2016-12-08 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208144414/http://money.cnn.com/2016/12/05/media/pizzagate-threatening-calls-washington-dc-businesses |archive-date=2016-12-08 |publisher=CNNMoney}}</ref>。這些公司接到大量具威脅性和恐嚇的電話，包括{{tsl|en|death threat|死亡威脅}}，甚至還受到網路滋擾<ref name="Kludt" />。小紅狐和泰拉索已向警方備案<ref name="Kludt" />。

