2016年12月4日，一名來自-{zh-cn:北卡罗来纳州; zh-tw:北卡羅萊納州; zh-hk:北卡羅萊納州;}-[[索爾茲伯里_(北卡羅來納州)|索爾茲伯里]]的28歲男子埃德加·麥迪遜·韋爾奇（{{lang|en|Edgar Maddison Welch}}）用{{tsl|en|AR-15 variant|AR-15式步槍}}向彗星乒乓的牆上、桌子和門各射了三槍<ref name=douglaswashburn /><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/fruzsinaeordogh/2016/12/07/with-pizzagate-is-cybersteria-the-new-normal/ |title=With Pizzagate, Is Cybersteria The New Normal? |last=Eordogh |first=Fruzsina |date=2016-12-07 |work=[[富比士|Forbes]] |access-date=2016-12-08 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161209174127/http://www.forbes.com/sites/fruzsinaeordogh/2016/12/07/with-pizzagate-is-cybersteria-the-new-normal/ |archive-date=2016-12-09}}</ref><ref name="HsuWelchPlea">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/comet-pizza-gunman-to-appear-at-plea-deal-hearing-friday-morning/2017/03/23/e12c91ba-0986-11e7-b77c-0047d15a24e0_story.html |title=Comet Pizza gunman pleads guilty to federal and local charges |last=Hsu |first=Spencer |date=2017-03-24 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324182045/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/comet-pizza-gunman-to-appear-at-plea-deal-hearing-friday-morning/2017/03/23/e12c91ba-0986-11e7-b77c-0047d15a24e0_story.html |archive-date=2017-03-24 |location=Washington}}</ref>。韋爾奇後來告訴警方他是對陰謀論作「自我調查」<ref name="Metro">{{Cite web |url=https://mpdc.dc.gov/release/arrest-made-assault-dangerous-weapon-gun-5000-block-connecticut-avenue-northwest |title=Arrest Made in an Assault with a Dangerous Weapon (Gun): 5000 Block of Connecticut Avenue, Northwest |date=2016-12-05 |website=mpdc |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219042253/http://mpdc.dc.gov/release/arrest-made-assault-dangerous-weapon-gun-5000-block-connecticut-avenue-northwest |archive-date=2016-12-19 |access-date=2020-01-27}}</ref>。韋爾奇視自己為故事中可能會拯救到孩童的英雄<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.csicop.org/si/show/pizzagate_and_beyond |title=Pizzagate and Beyond: Using Social Research to Understand Conspiracy Legends |last=Debies-Carl |first=Jeffrey |website=Center For Inquiry |access-date=2018-01-26 |archive-date=2018-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127004516/https://www.csicop.org/si/show/pizzagate_and_beyond |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在警察包圍餐廳後投降，並在沒有發生任何事件下被捕<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/latest-police-pizzeria-gunman-ar-15-rifle-handgun-43982089 |title=The Latest: Pizzagate Shooting Suspect Ordered Held by Judge |date=2016-12-05 |work=ABC News |access-date=2016-12-07 |dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206141536/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/latest-police-pizzeria-gunman-ar-15-rifle-handgun-43982089 |archive-date=2016-12-06}}</ref>。此次事件沒有人員傷亡<ref name="DCGunman">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/local/wp/2016/12/04/d-c-police-respond-to-report-of-a-man-with-a-gun-at-comet-ping-pong-restaurant/ |title=N.C. man told police he went to D.C. pizzeria with assault rifle to 'self-investigate' election-related conspiracy theory |last=Svrluga |first=Susan |date=2016-12-04 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |access-date=2016-12-29 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228095250/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/local/wp/2016/12/04/d-c-police-respond-to-report-of-a-man-with-a-gun-at-comet-ping-pong-restaurant/ |archive-date=2016-12-28 |last2=Siddiqui |first2=Faiz}}</ref>。

韋爾奇告訴警方，他曾在網上讀到彗星餐廳藏有兒童性奴隸，所以他想要親自看看他們是否在那裡<ref name="NY Times 2016-12-05">{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/05/business/media/comet-ping-pong-pizza-shooting-fake-news-consequences.html |title=In Washington Pizzeria Attack, Fake News Brought Real Guns |last=Kang |first=Cecilia |date=2016-12-05 |work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]] |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227204442/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/05/business/media/comet-ping-pong-pizza-shooting-fake-news-consequences.html |archive-date=2017-02-27 |last2=Goldman |first2=Adam}}</ref>。韋爾奇後來在接受《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》訪問時表示他對處理這種情況的形式感到後悔，但不會把這陰謀論摒棄在外，更拒絕將其稱為「假新聞」<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/07/us/edgar-welch-comet-pizza-fake-news.html |title=The Comet Ping Pong Gunman Answers Our Reporter's Questions |last=Goldman |first=Adam |date=2016-12-07 |work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]] |access-date=2016-12-14 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213214547/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/07/us/edgar-welch-comet-pizza-fake-news.html |archive-date=2016-12-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://time.com/4594988/pizzagate-gunman-comet-ping-pong-regret/ |title=Pizzagate Gunman: 'I Regret How I Handled' Comet Ping Pong Shooting |last=Abrams |first=Abigail |date=December 8, 2016 |work=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |access-date=2016-12-08 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208172642/http://time.com/4594988/pizzagate-gunman-comet-ping-pong-regret/ |archive-date=2016-12-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2016/12/08/pizzagate-gunman-says-regrets-how-handled-situation.html |title=Pizzagate gunman refuses to dismiss online conspiracy theory claims about child sex ring |date=2016-12-08 |access-date=2016-12-08 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208165849/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2016/12/08/pizzagate-gunman-says-regrets-how-handled-situation.html |archive-date=2016-12-08 |publisher=[[福斯新聞|Fox News]]}}</ref>。一些陰謀論者推測槍擊案是[[假旗行動|企圖分階段抹黑他們的調查]]<ref name="Gizmodo Pizzagaters" />。

2016年12月13日，韋爾奇被控「跨州運輸槍枝並意圖犯罪」（{{tsl|en|Federal crime in the United States|美國聯邦罪名|聯邦罪名}}）<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/12/13/505424283/pizzagate-suspect-faces-federal-charge |title='Pizzagate' Suspect Faces Federal Charge |last=Slotkin |first=Jason |date=2016-12-13 |access-date=2016-12-13 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214040314/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/12/13/505424283/pizzagate-suspect-faces-federal-charge |archive-date=2016-12-14 |publisher=NPR}}</ref>。根據法庭公文，韋爾奇嘗試在攻擊三天前招募朋友，並呼籲他們看有關陰謀的YouTube影片<ref name="iansimpson">{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-washingtondc-gunman-idUSKBN14213S |title=Accused 'fake-news' pizza gunman planned raid for days: affidavit |last=Simpson |first=Ian |date=2016-12-13 |access-date=2016-12-14 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214081418/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-washingtondc-gunman-idUSKBN14213S |archive-date=2016-12-14 |publisher=Reuters}}</ref>。他之後被控另外兩項罪名，{{tsl|en|Grand juries in the United States|美國大陪審團|大陪審團}}作出起訴，控告他在犯罪時使用危險武器襲擊並持有槍枝<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/u-s-grand-jury-returns-indictment-against-edgar-welch-in-comet-ping-pong-incursion/2016/12/15/e62118ac-c300-11e6-9578-0054287507db_story.html |title=Grand jury returns indictment against Edgar Welch in Comet Ping Pong incursion |last=Hsu |first=Spencer S. |date=2016-12-15 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220220559/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/u-s-grand-jury-returns-indictment-against-edgar-welch-in-comet-ping-pong-incursion/2016/12/15/e62118ac-c300-11e6-9578-0054287507db_story.html |archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/pizzagate-federal-charges_us_58502c44e4b0bd9c3dfef964 |title=Feds Escalate Charges Against Edgar Welch, Alleged 'Pizzagate' Shooter |last=Bellware |first=Kim |date=2016-12-13 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Huffington Post]] |access-date=2016-12-17 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161215151623/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/pizzagate-federal-charges_us_58502c44e4b0bd9c3dfef964 |archive-date=2016-12-15}}</ref>。2017年3月24日，韋爾奇在與檢察官達成[[認罪協商|認罪協商]]後，承認犯下聯邦指控的「跨州運輸槍枝」以及哥倫比亞特區指控的「使用危險武器襲擊」。韋爾奇還同意為餐廳的損失賠償5,744.33美元。美國地方法院法官[[凯坦吉·布朗·杰克森|凯坦吉·布朗·杰克森]]判他有期徒刑4年。在判決前聽審會上，韋爾奇對他的行為感到抱歉，並表示他「愚蠢又魯莽」<ref name="HsuWelchPlea" /><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/06/22/533941689/pizzagate-gunman-sentenced-to-4-years-in-prison |title='Pizzagate' Gunman Sentenced To 4 Years In Prison |work=NPR.org |access-date=2017-06-22 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622193717/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/06/22/533941689/pizzagate-gunman-sentenced-to-4-years-in-prison |archive-date=2017-06-22 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/pizzagate-gunman-sentenced-to-four-years-in-prison-as-prosecutors-urged-judge-to-deter-vigilante-justice/2017/06/22/a10db598-550b-11e7-ba90-f5875b7d1876_story.html |title='Pizzagate' gunman sentenced to four years in prison, as prosecutors urged judge to deter vigilante justice |last=Hsu |first=Spencer S. |date=2017-06-22 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622171606/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/pizzagate-gunman-sentenced-to-four-years-in-prison-as-prosecutors-urged-judge-to-deter-vigilante-justice/2017/06/22/a10db598-550b-11e7-ba90-f5875b7d1876_story.html |archive-date=2017-06-22}}</ref>。

2017年1月12日，一名來自[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[什里夫波特_(路易斯安那州)|什里夫波特]]的52歲男子约瑟夫·李·瓊斯（{{lang|en|Yusif Lee Jones}}）向[[美國路易斯安那西區聯邦地區法院|美國路易斯安那西區聯邦地區法院]]自首他曾在韋爾奇襲擊三天後打恐嚇電話給與彗星乒乓同個街區的野獸披薩。他表示曾向野獸披薩揚言要「拯救孩子」和「完成其他人沒做到的」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/cheats/2017/01/13/feds-louisiana-man-caught-making-new-pizzagate-threat.html |title=Feds: Louisiana Man Caught Making New 'PizzaGate' Threat |date=2017-01-13 |work=[[每日野獸|The Daily Beast]] |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116161856/http://www.thedailybeast.com/cheats/2017/01/13/feds-louisiana-man-caught-making-new-pizzagate-threat.html |archive-date=2017-01-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.justice.gov/usao-dc/pr/louisiana-man-pleads-guilty-federal-charge-threatening-pizza-shop-northwest-washington |title=Louisiana Man Pleads Guilty to Federal Charge For Threatening Pizza Shop in Northwest Washington (press release) |date=2017-01-13 |work=U.S. Department of Justice |access-date=2020-09-09 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202030151/https://www.justice.gov/usao-dc/pr/louisiana-man-pleads-guilty-federal-charge-threatening-pizza-shop-northwest-washington|archive-date=2017-02-02}}</ref>。

2019年1月25日，彗星乒乓的其中一間裡屋遭到縱火。員工們迅速撲滅火勢，並沒有人員傷亡<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/fire-at-comet-ping-pong-was-intentionally-set-fire-and-police-officials-say/2019/01/25/d0b09896-201c-11e9-8e21-59a09ff1e2a1_story.html|title=Fire at Comet Ping Pong was intentionally set, fire and police officials say|date=2019-01-26|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|access-date=2020-09-09|last=Hermann|first=Peter|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511131943/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/fire-at-comet-ping-pong-was-intentionally-set-fire-and-police-officials-say/2019/01/25/d0b09896-201c-11e9-8e21-59a09ff1e2a1_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

