publisher=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]}}</ref>、倫敦的《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/donald-trump-russia-us-election-intervene-hacks-cyberattacks-dnc-podesta-emails-leak-help-victory-a7466986.html |title=Donald Trump's transition team dismisses CIA findings Russia attempted to influence US election in his favour |last=Dearden |first=Lizzie |date=2016-12-10 |work=[[獨立報|The Independent]] |access-date=2016-12-23 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220193532/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/donald-trump-russia-us-election-intervene-hacks-cyberattacks-dnc-podesta-emails-leak-help-victory-a7466986.html |archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref>、《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/trump-national-security-monica-crowley_us_58542a74e4b08debb788afc4 |title=Yet Another Donald Trump Pick Has A Habit Of Spreading Dangerous Conspiracy Theories |date=2016-12-16 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223110925/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/trump-national-security-monica-crowley_us_58542a74e4b08debb788afc4 |archive-date=2016-12-23 |publisher=[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]}}</ref>、《[[華盛頓時報|華盛頓時報]]》<ref name="TWT1">{{Cite news |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2016/dec/9/alex-jones-conspiracy-theorist-appeals-trump-aid-o/ |title=Infowars' Alex Jones appeals to Trump for aid over fears of 'fake news' crackdown |last=Blake |first=Andrew |date=2016-12-09 |access-date=2016-12-10 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161209224504/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2016/dec/9/alex-jones-conspiracy-theorist-appeals-trump-aid-o/ |archive-date=2016-12-09 |publisher=[[華盛頓時報|The Washington Times]]}}</ref>、《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-fake-news-guide-2016-story.html |title=Where fake news came from — and why some readers believe it |last=Agrawal |first=Nina |date=2016-12-20 |work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] |access-date=2016-12-23 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222223616/http://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-fake-news-guide-2016-story.html |archive-date=2016-12-22}}</ref>、《[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]》<ref name="Fox">{{Cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2016/12/05/man-with-rifle-arrested-at-dc-restaurant-targeted-by-fake-news-conspiracy-theories.html |title=Man with rifle arrested at DC restaurant targeted by fake news conspiracy theories |date=2016-12-05 |access-date=2016-12-09 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207164759/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2016/12/05/man-with-rifle-arrested-at-dc-restaurant-targeted-by-fake-news-conspiracy-theories.html |archive-date=2016-12-07 |publisher=[[福斯新聞頻道|Fox News]] }}</ref>、[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://money.cnn.com/2016/12/05/media/fake-news-real-violence-pizzagate/index.html |title=Fake news, real violence: 'Pizzagate' and the consequences of an Internet echo chamber |last=Stelter |first=Brian |work=CNNMoney |date=2016-12-06 |access-date=2018-11-05 |archive-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105202529/https://money.cnn.com/2016/12/05/media/fake-news-real-violence-pizzagate/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和《{{tsl|en|Miami Herald|邁阿密先驅報}}》<ref name="hannahalam">{{Cite news |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/news/nation-world/national/article119065843.html |title=Conspiracy peddlers continue pushing debunked 'pizzagate' tale |last=Alam |first=Hannah |date=2016-12-05 |work=Miami Herald |access-date=2016-12-07 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207152446/http://www.miamiherald.com/news/nation-world/national/article119065843.html |archive-date=2016-12-07}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Metropolitan Police Department of the District of Columbia|哥倫比亞特區首都警察局}}稱此事為「捏造」<ref name=hannahalam /><section begin="debunk" /><section end="debunk" />。

陰謀論的擁護者引用的許多謠傳的證據均來自完全不同的來源，並讓它看起來好像在支持陰謀<ref name="snopes" />。他們聲稱是受害者的照片是從[[社交媒體|社交媒體]]（如[[Instagram|Instagram]]）擷取披薩店員工的家人和朋友<ref name="FALSE" />。《{{tsl|en|The Charlotte Observer|夏洛特觀察報}}》指出揭穿陰謀論的各種信息來源，並指出這包括了除《紐約時報》之外的[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]<ref name="douglaswashburn">{{Cite news |url=http://www.courier-tribune.com/news/20161206/religious-zeal-drives-nc-man-in-8216pizzagate8217 |title=Religious zeal drives N.C. man in 'Pizzagate' |last=Douglas |first=William |date=2016-12-06 |work=The Courier-Tribune |access-date=2016-12-07 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208131816/http://www.courier-tribune.com/news/20161206/religious-zeal-drives-nc-man-in-8216pizzagate8217 |archive-date=2016-12-08 |agency=The Charlotte Observer |last2=Washburn |first2=Mark }}</ref>。

2016年12月10日，《紐約時報》發表了一篇分析理論主張的文章<ref name="NYTDebunk" />。他們強調：

* 陰謀論者透過彗星乒乓的標誌以及[[撒旦崇拜|撒旦崇拜]]和戀童癖的象徵之間的相似性，所以將公司和陰謀扯上關係。然而，《泰晤士報》指出許多不相關公司的標誌也找得到相似之處，例如[[美國線上|美國線上]]、[[華納媒體|華納媒體]]和[[MSN|MSN]]<ref name="NYTDebunk" />。
* 陰謀論者聲稱彗星乒乓的地下室是一系列交易的核心。但這家餐廳實際上根本沒有地下室，而且圖片用來支撐主張的是在另一個場所拍的<ref name="NYTDebunk" />。
* 陰謀論者聲稱有餐廳老闆阿萊凡蒂斯身穿有宣傳戀童癖T恤的照片。然而，這張圖是另一個人，而那件衣服是印著「J' ❤ L'Enfant」，其實是代表特區的殷范提咖啡店與酒吧（{{lang|en|L'Enfant Cafe-Bar}}，以參與華盛頓哥倫比亞特區大多佈局的設計師{{tsl|en|Pierre Charles L'Enfant|皮爾‧查爾斯‧殷范提}}命名），而老闆就是照片中的人<ref name="NYTDebunk" />。
* 陰謀論者聲稱[[約翰·波德斯塔|約翰]]和{{tsl|en|Tony Podesta|東尼·波德斯塔}}綁架了[[馬德琳·麥卡恩失蹤事件|馬德琳·-{zh-hans:麦卡恩; zh-hant:麥肯;}-]]並利用警察素描逃脫，實際上，同一名嫌疑人的兩張素描是來自兩名目擊者的描述<ref name="NYTDebunk" />。

沒有所謂的受害者站出來，也沒找到任何物證<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/pizzagate-conspiracy-theories-michael-flynn-junior-1.3883406 |title='Pizzagate': How a WikiLeaks-fuelled conspiracy theory led to gunfire at a D.C. restaurant |last=Barakat |first=Matthew |date=December 6, 2016 |access-date=2016-12-13 |dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213001049/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/pizzagate-conspiracy-theories-michael-flynn-junior-1.3883406 |archive-date=2016-12-13 |publisher=CBC News |last2=Gresko |first2=Jessica}}</ref>。

